    <item>
      <title>为什么三重巫师日对华尔街如此重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-21/why-triple-witching-day-matters-on-wall-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街又迎来了“三重巫师日”。根据期权平台 SpotGamma 的估计，与指数、股票和交易所交易基金挂钩的价值约 5.5 万亿美元的期权将到期。彭博社的西蒙·怀特在“彭博简报”中解释了这一切为何如此重要。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-21/why-triple-witching-day-matters-on-wall-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 13:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
